				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Soulpiercer or 1H Velium Gemmed?<a name="69857"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Nov 17 04 6:56 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I won soulpiercer in WoS a few weeks ago.  I like it.  I sold my velium gemmed sword and use soulpiercer in my primary slot.  Both are very simular in DPS and stats, but Soulpeircer procs rune I.  It procs quite a bit during fights.  It does NOT use a reagent like the description says BTW.
<br />

<br />
Rune I is just 55 HP but lasts 30 minutes if youre not hit.  If you get hit during melee then it will refresh on the next proc.  This is not a lot, but hey, it's free HP.  Soulpiercer has a +80 HP stat but because of the Rune I proc its really more. Thats how I thought about it and decided it was better than velium gemmed.
<br />

<br />
As for looks, soulpiercer looks a lot like velium gemmed.  It has a slightly more intracate design but has no colors.  Its silver just like many weapons.
<br />

<br />
Dumaine</span></td>
